data.description: Great structurally sound 4 sided brick ranch on full finished basement sitting on 4.4 private wooded acres with two entrances. Large outbuilding for workshop or garage for additional parking or even a barn for horses. Open floor plan with large family room, lvp flooring, kitchen has brick backsplash and bar area, oversized pantry and laundry room, Master bedroom features sitting area, master bath with tile shower, guest bath has large vanity area. Full basement has kitchen area with bar, family room, bedroom and full bath and large patio for entertaining. Home has 2 septic tank, 2 hot water heaters and also an additional well for watering plants, garden etc. Custom built kids playhouse. Property backs up to hundreds of acres of conservation. Large barn or workshop. Great property for mini farm. Feels like country but so close to shopping, church, restaurants ets...
